####
#### Update un nouveau contact
####
PATCH {{hostname}}/contacts/{{{{codeContact}}}} HTTP/1.1
X-API-Key: no-key-at-all
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nom": "Reis",
    "prenom" : "Nando",
