####
#### Delete un contact
####
DELETE {{hostname}}/contacts/{{codeContact}} HTTP/1.1
X-API-Key: no-key-at-all
Content-Type: application/json

####
#### Delete tous les contacts
####
DELETE {{hostname}}/contacts HTTP/1.1
X-API-Key: no-key-at-all
Content-Type: application/json